---
import EventLayout from "../../components/EventLayout.astro";

const images = [
  { src: "/ap-workshop/photo_2026-03-08 19.50.40.jpeg", alt: "University Robotics Workshop" },
];
---

<EventLayout
  title="University Robotics Workshop"
  date="February 10, 2026"
  location="AP Hogeschool, Antwerp"
  type="Workshop"
  description="Hands-on SO-101 robotics workshop at AP Hogeschool covering the LeRobot ecosystem, VLAs, and imitation learning workflows."
  images={images}
>
  <p>A hands-on workshop at AP Hogeschool Antwerpen where students got their first exposure to the LeRobot ecosystem. We covered SO-101 arms, vision-language-action models (VLAs), and the imitation learning workflows that make modern robotics accessible.</p>
  <p>Education is one of our core commitments. Bringing robotics directly into university classrooms bridges the gap between what students learn and what the industry actually needs.</p>
</EventLayout>
